{
  "stem": "2833.3",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But he had no idea of, you know, of those things, that it's possible that somebody can live like this.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So whenever we asked for something which would be the normal thing for everybody to have, he thought we should make do, till I explained to him that all these things are not something that we have seen in a long, long time.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And one day that little young GI at the gate was there again.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he called me and said, I have something for you.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I said, what?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So he pulled out a ring.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he hands me the ring and says, this should bring you luck that you get home and find your family.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I don't know where he got the ring from, but it was very sweet.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So that was--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then when they told us they would take us home to wherever, you know, we come from or wherever we want to go.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I had a young girl with me in my group who was married in Theresien.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She came from Westerbork, Holland, but she actually was from Germany.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Had gone to Holland to save herself, and of course, that didn't work.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So she came there and married a Czech young man in Theresien.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So she came home with us because she had no family, looking for her husband.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So she came and we were taken by bus by-- from the Americans. to the-- Czechoslovakia to-- was divided at that time, American and Russian.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So they took us to the little town where the Russians were already.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they put us on the train and took us to Prague.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And all the way on the train where-- every little town, we had to stop, because people came, brought us food.",
      "word_count": 21
    }
  ],
